data.description: Gorgeous Oakland Acres home! Three bedrooms, three bathrooms. As you walk through the front door, you enter a spacious living room that boasts a vaulted ceiling, electric fireplace and beautiful laminate flooring. Continuing into the kitchen, you will immediately notice the hickory cabinets and nice-sized island. The main floor master bedroom and bathroom are conveniently located just steps away from the kitchen and living room. Heading upstairs, you will find two nice-sized bedrooms and a full bathroom. The basement is a great space for entertaining as it has a large family room, wet bar, and full bathroom. The laundry room is also located in the basement. There is geothermal heat and cooling which makes the utility bills very affordable. The views from the deck are amazing. Call today for a showing!
